{"tid":2023446,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[身先士卒]特朗普透露正服用抗瘧疾藥物「羥氯喹」預防武漢肺炎病毒 (09:18)","createTime":"2020-05-19T04:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T06:34:59.000Z","uid":57677,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"19e85842438c867a89f22b05659da62b5f9575d8","tid":2023446,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:22:49.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普周一（18日）在白宮會見餐飲業界時透露，自己正服用抗瘧疾藥物「羥氯喹」（hydroxychloroquine）和鋅補充劑。但不少美國專家均稱這種藥物對預防新型冠狀病毒毫無作用。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普稱，過去一個半星期每天服用一粒羥氯喹，被問及白宮醫生是否推薦他服用該藥物，特朗普說：「醫生沒有推薦，但說『好吧，如果你想的話』。」他亦稱曾服用一劑抗生素阿奇霉素（azithromycin），以預防新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普早前曾稱羥氯喹或可治療新冠病毒，但之後有研究稱該藥物沒有幫助。美國食品及藥物管理局（FDA）上月24日曾警告，新冠病毒患者服用羥氯喹或氯喹（chloroquine）會有嚴重心律不正的問題。<br />\n（路透社）"},{"pid":"d468872799eadd1f92d1c5b74fa9fa3ef2974eb8","tid":2023446,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:26:46.000Z","msg":"有冇ching食過羥氯喹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39526a9a53b6ac780ee06f59ec821048ff85c190","tid":2023446,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:32:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">光復香港，要你幫手！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【丫叉郵包案】<span style=\"color: orange;\">眾籌民事訴訟控告警方</span></strong><br />\n眾籌連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cMLSEJ&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2Fwb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=a79a38b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【612基金】<span style=\"color: orange;\">大量手足上庭，基金只剩幾三千萬！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://612fund.hk/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2Fdonate&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2Fwb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=5575bb22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://612fund.hk/donate</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【星火】<span style=\"color: orange;\">以新模式運作，接受